text: Maria Anna of Bavaria may refer to: *Maria Anna of Bavaria (1551–1608), who married her uncle Charles II, Archduke of Austria *Maria Anna of Bavaria (1574–1616), who married Ferdinand II, Holy Roman Emperor, niece of the above *Duchess Maria Anna of Bavaria, married Louis, Dauphin of France (1661–1711), great-granddaughter of the first, grandniece of the above *Maria Anna of Bavaria (1805-1877), who married Frederick Augustus II of Saxony *Maria Anna of Bavaria (b. 1975), youngest daughter of Prince Max, Duke in Bavaria.
title: Maria Anna of Bavaria
